OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774192264
OL,3,C'A great match became a mismatch':
OL,4,CNewcastle United's 7-2 defeat to
OL,5,CBarcelona
OL,7,FIn the immortal words of cinema's
OL,8,Fgreatest fictional TV Presenter,
OL,9,FAnchorman's Ron Burgundy: "Boy, that
OL,10,Fescalated quickly. I mean, that really
OL,11,Fgot out of hand fast."
OL,13,FNewcastle United are out of the
OL,14,FChampions League after a fever dream
OL,15,Fat the Camp Nou.
OL,17,FThere they were, a little unlucky to
OL,18,Fbe 3-2 down at half time after a
OL,19,Fbreathless, brilliant first half in
OL,20,Fwhich they'd landed some serious
OL,21,Fpunches on Barcelona, in Barcelona.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
