FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774192264
OL,3,C'A great match became a mismatch':
OL,4,CNewcastle United's 7-2 defeat to
OL,5,CBarcelona
OL,7,FBut a little more than 10 minutes into
OL,8,Fthe second half the game and the tie
OL,9,Fhad gone. Fast forward another 15
OL,10,Fminutes and everything had gone,
OL,11,Fincluding discipline and dignity.
OL,13,FFor those who grew up with old
OL,14,Ffashioned football scores on telly, or
OL,15,Fin the papers, Barcelona needed
OL,16,Fbrackets. 7(seven)-2.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
