OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774192264
OL,3,C'A great match became a mismatch':
OL,4,CNewcastle United's 7-2 defeat to
OL,5,CBarcelona
OL,7,FThe Magpies were good enough to match
OL,8,FBarcelona from gun to tape in last
OL,9,Fweek's first leg at St James Park, but
OL,10,Fonly good enough to match them for
OL,11,Fhalf a game at the Camp Nou.
OL,13,FNewcastle were motoring, then they
OL,14,Fconked out. A great match became a
OL,15,Fmismatch. You could say it was a
OL,16,Ftactical thing, a squad thing, a
OL,17,Fschedule thing or a fatigue thing.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
