FL,429,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774192264
OL,3,C'A great match became a mismatch':
OL,4,CNewcastle United's 7-2 defeat to
OL,5,CBarcelona
OL,7,FYou can point out that Barcelona are
OL,8,Fjust fundamentally the better side.
OL,9,FBut none of that really explains the
OL,10,FJekyll and Hyde scenario that unfolded.
OL,12,FIt was just a game of two halves I
OL,13,Fsuppose (sorry).
OL,15,FWe all wondered beforehand if the
OL,16,FMagpies could win and for a while it
OL,17,Flooked like they could.
OL,19,FIt turned out they couldn't.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
