PN,42805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1774192264
OL,3,C'A great match became a mismatch':
OL,4,CNewcastle United's 7-2 defeat to
OL,5,CBarcelona
OL,7,FIt was tough on Newcastle's
OL,8,Fmagnificent travelling fans who had
OL,9,Fhope one minute and nothing the next.
OL,10,FBut this Champions League campaign has
OL,11,Fbeen an often joyful endeavour and
OL,12,Fanother useful learning curve.
OL,14,FEveryone in Black and White enjoyed
OL,15,Fmixing with European Football royalty
OL,16,Fthis week, but they left with a
OL,17,Freminder of how far away they still
OL,18,Fare from joining the elite.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
